<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NSL Personalkampagne - Fair Recruitment</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --nsl-red: #cc1f1f;
            --nsl-gold: #f2a900;
            --nsl-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --nsl-light: #f5f5f5;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #e0e0e0;
            color: var(--nsl-dark);
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact !important;
            print-color-adjust: exact !important;
        }
        .page {
            width: 297mm;
            height: 210mm; /* A4 Landscape */
            background: white;
            margin: 20px auto;
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            page-break-after: always;
        }
        @media print {
            html, body { background: white; margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }
            .page { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-shadow: none; width: 100%; height: 100%; page-break-after: always; page-break-inside: avoid; border: none; border-radius: 0; }
            @page { size: landscape; margin: 0; }
            .top-controls { display: none !important; }
        }
        
        /* Layout Utils */
        .flex { display: flex; }
        .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; height: 100%; }
        .col-left { padding: 40px; background: var(--nsl-dark); color: white; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
        .col-right { padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; }
        
        .header {
            position: absolute;
            top: 40px; left: 40px; right: 40px;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        
        h1 { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.1; text-transform: uppercase; }
        h2 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: var(--nsl-red); text-transform: uppercase; }
        h3 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: var(--nsl-gold); }
        p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0; }
        ul { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; padding-left: 20px; }
        ul li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        
        .highlight { color: var(--nsl-red); }
        .highlight-gold { color: var(--nsl-gold); }
        
        .feature-box {
            background: var(--nsl-light);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--nsl-red);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        .feature-box h4 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--nsl-dark); }
        .feature-box p { font-size: 16px; margin: 0; color: #555; }

        /* Graphics Patterns */
        .bg-pattern {
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%; right: -20%;
            width: 800px; height: 800px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(242,169,0,0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 70%);
        }

        .top-controls {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .lang-switch { display: flex; gap: 5px; }
        .lang-btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .lang-btn.active { background: var(--nsl-dark); color: white; }
        .print-btn {
            background: var(--nsl-red); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 5px 15px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .print-btn:hover { background: #a11818; }
        .home-btn {
            background: var(--nsl-dark); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 5px 15px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .home-btn:hover { background: #000; }
        @media print { .top-controls { display: none !important; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="top-controls">
        <a href="/" class="home-btn">← Back to Login</a>
        <div class="lang-switch">
            <a href="?lang=de" class="lang-btn <%= lang === 'de' ? 'active' : '' %>">DE</a>
            <a href="?lang=en" class="lang-btn <%= lang === 'en' ? 'active' : '' %>">EN</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 1: Introduction -->
    <div class="page grid-2" style="background: var(--nsl-light);">
        <div class="col-left" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2a2a2a 100%);">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                <img src="/assets/design/NSL_logo_mid.png" alt="NSL Click & Work" style="height: 60px;">
                <img src="/assets/design/Logo_Mid_PersonalKampagne.png" alt="PersonalKampagne" style="height: 35px;" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
            </div>
            <h3 class="highlight-gold">FAIR RECRUITMENT</h3>
            <h1 style="white-space: nowrap;">NSL Personal<br>Campaign</h1>
            <p style="color: #ccc; font-size: 20px; max-width: 90%;">Sustainable skills placement through Fair Recruitment.<br>Transparent processes creating win-win situations for employers and professionals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-right" style="background: var(--nsl-red); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
            <div class="bg-pattern"></div>
            <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
                <h2 style="color: white; font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 20px;">The "Employer Pays" Principle</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 0 40px;">
                    NSL Click & Work and our partner employers across Germany strictly follow the <strong>"Employer Pays"</strong> principle. <br><br>
                    This means that all costs associated with recruitment are never transferred to healthcare professionals.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 2: Declaration of Principles -->
    <div class="page grid-2" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; background: white;">
        <div class="col-left" style="background: var(--nsl-light); color: var(--nsl-dark); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
            <div style="padding: 20px;">
                <h3 class="highlight-gold">CORE STANDARDS</h3>
                <h2 style="font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--nsl-red);">Declaration of Principles.</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    We aim to offer a socially sustainable perspective to both professionals and healthcare/educational institutions in Germany. Our work is based on fairness and transparency.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 18px;">
                    We adhere to high ethical and professional standards, which include the core principles listed here.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-right">
            <div class="feature-box" style="background: transparent; border-color: var(--nsl-red); padding-left: 0; border: none; border-left: 6px solid var(--nsl-red); padding-left: 20px;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 20px;">Written Documentation</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">For the complete verifiability of all contract terms between all parties.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box" style="background: transparent; border-color: var(--nsl-gold); padding-left: 0; border: none; border-left: 6px solid var(--nsl-gold); padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 20px;">Zero Fees</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Zero fees for nursing professionals throughout the entire placement process.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box" style="background: transparent; border-color: var(--nsl-dark); padding-left: 0; border: none; border-left: 6px solid var(--nsl-dark); padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 20px;">Risk Limitation</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Limitation of economic risk for nursing professionals.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box" style="background: transparent; border-color: var(--nsl-red); padding-left: 0; border: none; border-left: 6px solid var(--nsl-red); padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 20px;">Full Transparency</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Transparency regarding structures, services, and costs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE 3: Global Guidelines & Complaint -->
    <div class="page grid-2" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; background: var(--nsl-red);">
        <div class="col-left" style="background: white; color: var(--nsl-dark); padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
            <h3 class="highlight-gold">GLOBAL GUIDELINES</h3>
            <h2 style="font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 30px;">International Conventions.</h2>
            
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Our code of conduct is based on the <strong>WHO Code of Conduct for the International Recruitment of Health Personnel</strong>.
            </p>
            
            <div class="feature-box" style="background: transparent; border-color: var(--nsl-red); padding-left: 0; border: none; border-left: 6px solid var(--nsl-red); padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 20px;">No Critical Shortage Countries</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">NSL recruits exclusively from countries not classified by the WHO as having a critical shortage of health workers.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-box" style="background: transparent; border-color: var(--nsl-gold); padding-left: 0; border: none; border-left: 6px solid var(--nsl-gold); padding-left: 20px;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 20px;">Human Rights Compliance</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">We commit to complying with international human rights conventions, the ILO Core Labor Standards, and the IRIS Standards of the IOM.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-right" style="background: var(--nsl-dark); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start;">
            <h3 class="highlight-gold">GET IN TOUCH</h3>
            <h2 style="font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 30px; color: white;">Complaint Procedure.</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                We hereby inform you that you have the right to lodge a complaint if there are any irregularities in the placement process. Your complaint will be treated confidentially and processed within a maximum of three weeks.
            </p>
            
            <div style="background: var(--nsl-red); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
                <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: white; font-size: 20px;">Contact Management</h4>
                <p style="margin: 0; color: white; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">
                    info@newsolution.eu
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
